---
import { VERSION, BUILD } from '../lib/version';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Distinction Physics</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A meta-theoretical framework deriving the structure of accessible reality from two axioms about distinction-making under energy constraints.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Sora:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Distinction Physics</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Reality under resource constraints</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
      <section class="intro">
        <p class="lead">
          A meta-theoretical framework that derives the structure of accessible reality from two axioms:
        </p>
        <div class="axioms">
          <div class="axiom">
            <span class="axiom-number">A1</span>
            <span class="axiom-text">All distinctions cost energy</span>
          </div>
          <div class="axiom">
            <span class="axiom-number">A2</span>
            <span class="axiom-text">All observers have finite energy budgets</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="consequence">
          From these alone, we derive quantization, uncertainty, entropy, consciousness, and the structure of spacetime—not as separate mysteries, but as necessary consequences of finite-energy distinction-making.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="entry-points">
        <a href="/essay" class="entry-card primary">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"/>
              <path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2>Read the Essay</h2>
            <p>The complete framework in 13 sections, from philosophical foundations through quantum mechanics, consciousness, and spacetime.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/explore" class="entry-card secondary">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"/>
              <path d="M2 12h20"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2>Explore Concepts</h2>
            <p>Browse the key propositions as a network of interconnected ideas. Each concept linked to its logical dependencies.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/treatise" class="entry-card treatise">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="card-content">
            <h2>Academic Treatise</h2>
            <p>The full scholarly treatment with formal definitions, theorems, derivations, and rigorous mathematical apparatus.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="card-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </section>

      <section class="status-block">
        <div class="status-header">
          <span class="status-label">Framework Status</span>
          <span class="status-badge">V7 · Anti-fragile</span>
        </div>
        <p class="status-text">
          This framework has survived 36 adversarial attacks across 7 rounds of systematic critique.
          Every attack either failed or generated refinements. The transcendental core—that distinction is
          necessary for any thought or experience—cannot be attacked without using distinction.
        </p>
        <div class="status-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">36</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Attacks Survived</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">28</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Antibodies Generated</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-value">22</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Refinements Absorbed</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <span class="version-info">{VERSION} · build {BUILD}</span>
        <span class="footer-text">Working Draft · December 2025</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    --void: #0a0a0c;
    --depth-1: #12121a;
    --depth-2: #1a1a24;
    --border: #2a2a3a;
    --text-primary: #e8e8f0;
    --text-secondary: #a0a0b8;
    --text-muted: #606080;
    --accent: #4a9eff;
    --accent-dim: rgba(74, 158, 255, 0.15);
    --font-display: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    --font-body: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    background: var(--void);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .container {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--depth-1) 0%, var(--void) 100%);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .main-content {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem 4rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .axioms {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .axiom {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--depth-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .axiom-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--accent-dim);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .axiom-text {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .consequence {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .entry-points {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .entry-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    background: var(--depth-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .entry-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--depth-2);
  }

  .entry-card.primary {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--depth-1) 0%, var(--accent-dim) 100%);
  }

  .entry-card.treatise {
    border-color: #50c878;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--depth-1) 0%, rgba(80, 200, 120, 0.08) 100%);
  }

  .entry-card.treatise .card-icon {
    color: #50c878;
  }

  .card-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .card-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .card-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .card-content p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .card-arrow {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .entry-card:hover .card-arrow {
    transform: translateX(4px);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .status-block {
    background: var(--depth-1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .status-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .status-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .status-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #50c878;
    background: rgba(80, 200, 120, 0.15);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .status-text {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .status-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .site-footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .entry-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card-arrow {
      display: none;
    }

    .status-stats {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
